Whether your home is now an office, classroom, gym or all of the above – Computer Mania can help keep you connected with essential products & solutions. You can now purchase essential connectivity products in Computer Mania’s online store and have it delivered to your door. This includes hardware and software, consumables like printer cartridges, and more! Customers in possession of an Essential Services permit can now make use of a drop-off and collect repair service in Brooklyn (Pretoria) and Montague Gardens (Cape Town). To access this service, you simply have to phone in beforehand and take along your permit. For contact details, visit the Computer Mania website. Visit Computer Mania’s website for more details, and to discover a few other ways to stay connected to your world. This article was published in partnership with Computer Mania.